{"type":"excalidraw","version":2,"source":"excalidraw-diagram-skill","elements":[{"type":"rectangle","id":"darkbg","x":-4000,"y":-3000,"width":10000,"height":7500,"backgroundColor":"#1e1e2e","fillStyle":"solid","strokeColor":"transparent","strokeWidth":0,"roughness":1,"opacity":100},{"type":"text","id":"title","x":120,"y":10,"width":430,"height":30,"text":"TextField vs TextFormField 선택 기준","fontSize":22,"strokeColor":"#e5e5e5","fontFamily":2,"roughness":1,"opacity":100},{"type":"rectangle","id":"left","x":30,"y":55,"width":300,"height":170,"backgroundColor":"#1e3a5f","fillStyle":"solid","roundness":{"type":3},"strokeColor":"#4a9eed","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"opacity":100},{"type":"text","id":"left_t","x":120,"y":60,"width":140,"height":25,"text":"TextField","fontSize":17,"strokeColor":"#4a9eed","fontFamily":2,"textAlign":"center","roughness":1,"opacity":100},{"type":"text","id":"left_items","x":50,"y":90,"width":260,"height":120,"text":"• Form 없이 단독 사용\n• TextEditingController로\n  값 직접 관리\n• 실시간 입력 처리,\n  검색 바, 채팅 입력에 적합\n• 유효성 검사를 직접 구현","fontSize":13,"strokeColor":"#a0a0a0","fontFamily":2,"roughness":1,"opacity":100},{"type":"rectangle","id":"right","x":370,"y":55,"width":300,"height":170,"backgroundColor":"#2d1b69","fillStyle":"solid","roundness":{"type":3},"strokeColor":"#8b5cf6","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"opacity":100},{"type":"text","id":"right_t","x":440,"y":60,"width":180,"height":25,"text":"TextFormField","fontSize":17,"strokeColor":"#8b5cf6","fontFamily":2,"textAlign":"center","roughness":1,"opacity":100},{"type":"text","id":"right_items","x":390,"y":90,"width":260,"height":120,"text":"• 반드시 Form 위젯 안에서 사용\n• validator·onSaved 콜백 내장\n• Form 전체 일괄 검증\n  (validate()) 가능\n• 로그인·회원가입·설정 등\n  폼 화면에 적합","fontSize":13,"strokeColor":"#a0a0a0","fontFamily":2,"roughness":1,"opacity":100}],"appState":{"viewBackgroundColor":"#1e1e2e"}}